---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SOP-1 · 客户发现 (调研中)" active="scoring">
  <section class="poster-section admin-section sop-page">
    <nav class="sop-tabs sop-tabs--global" aria-label="SOP navigation">
      <a href="/admin/scoring" class="sop-tab">
        <span class="sop-tab-id">📊 概览</span>
        <span class="sop-tab-zh">销售流水线总览</span>
        <span class="sop-tab-en">Overview</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-1" class="sop-tab sop-tab--active" aria-current="page">
        <span class="sop-tab-id">🎣 SOP-1</span>
        <span class="sop-tab-zh">客户发现</span>
        <span class="sop-tab-en">Intake & Discovery</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-2" class="sop-tab">
        <span class="sop-tab-id">🔍 SOP-2</span>
        <span class="sop-tab-zh">筛选 + 审计</span>
        <span class="sop-tab-en">Screening & Audit</span>
      </a>
    </nav>
    <div class="admin-shell lead-admin-shell scoring-shell sop-shell" data-ui-version="local-style-2026-05-08">
      <header class="admin-header">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">SOP-1 · 客户发现 INTAKE & DISCOVERY</p>
          <h1>客户发现 / Intake & Discovery</h1>
          <p class="zh-en-sub"><span>Lead Intake &amp; Discovery</span>　·　<span class="micro">"我们怎么找客户" — 抓客户进入数据库的第一段</span></p>
          <p class="lede">把候选客户从外面（Google Maps / 图片 / 关键词搜索）抓进 entity 数据库。所有入口最终统一进 V2 entity store，下游 SOP-2 筛选 + 审计完全一致。</p>
          <div class="sop2-doc-link-row">
            <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-1-doc" class="sop2-doc-link-btn">
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-icon">📘</span>
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-text">
                <strong>SOP-1 详细文档 v1.0</strong>
                <span class="sop2-doc-link-sub">source of truth · <code>docs/SOP_1_INTAKE_DISCOVERY.md</code></span>
              </span>
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="sop2-doc-link-row">
            <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-handoff-doc" class="sop2-doc-link-btn">
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-icon">📑</span>
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-text">
                <strong>SOP-1 → SOP-2 数据交接合约 / Handoff Contract</strong>
                <span class="sop2-doc-link-sub">SOP-1 出口契约 · entity schema 每字段解读 · 必填校验</span>
              </span>
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="sop2-doc-link-row">
            <a href="#investigation-note" class="sop2-doc-link-btn">
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-icon">📋</span>
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-text">
                <strong>SOP-1 调研笔记 (待 review)</strong>
                <span class="sop2-doc-link-sub">现状摸底 · 6 个检查点等你回 · <code>data/qa/sop-investigations/sop-1.md</code></span>
              </span>
              <span class="sop2-doc-link-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="admin-page-meta">
            <span class="admin-page-version">v1.0</span>
            <span class="dot">·</span>
            <span class="admin-page-updated">最近更新 2026-05-12</span>
            <span class="dot">·</span>
            <span>G-1 / G-2 / G-3 / G-6 ✅</span>
          </p>
          <div class="admin-code-sync-banner is-synced">
            <span>✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong>页面与代码同步</strong> — G-1 <code>pl:scrape-docker</code> · G-2 <code>pl:preflight</code> · G-3 <code>entity.batch_id</code> · G-6 image-lead V2 (<code>pl:ingest-image</code>) · <strong>G-7 Places enrichment (<code>pl:places-enrich</code>)</strong> 均已落地。<br/>
              完整内容见 <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-1-doc">SOP-1 详细文档 v1.0</a>。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="admin-count">
          <span>当前状态</span>
          <strong>🟡 调研中</strong>
          <span class="micro-note">等 Matthew review<br/>4-step 协议 Step 2</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- ─── 4-step SOP 协议进度 (stage-grid pattern, SOP-2 同款) ───────── -->
      <section class="admin-paper-section">
        <div class="admin-paper-section-head">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">4-step SOP 协议 · 当前进度</p>
            <h2>SOP-1 还在 Step 2 <span class="en-sub">Awaiting your review of the investigation note</span></h2>
          </div>
          <span class="admin-section-count">4 step · Step 2 active</span>
        </div>
        <p class="section-lede">建任何 SOP 必须走完 4 步：调研 → review → 写 → 验证。SOP-1 调研笔记已完成（实测 gosom Docker + grep 代码 + 20 leads scrape），等你 review 回答 6 个检查点，才动手写 v0.1。</p>

        <div class="stage-grid">
          <div class="stage-card stage-done">
            <div class="stage-num">Step 1<span class="stage-cond-badge">完成</span></div>
            <div class="stage-name">现状调研<span class="stage-en">Investigation</span></div>
            <div class="stage-desc">
              <p class="stage-desc-zh">读相关代码 · 探 Docker 容器 · 跑 verify scrape (实测 20 leads / 3 分钟) · grep search/enrichment 模块清单。</p>
              <p class="stage-desc-en"><span class="lang-tag">EN</span> Read code · test Docker · live scrape sample → investigation note</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stage-meta">
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">产出</span> <code>data/qa/sop-investigations/sop-1.md</code> (~290 行)</div>
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">状态</span> <span class="chip chip-mint">完成 ✅</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stage-card stage-active">
            <div class="stage-num">Step 2<span class="stage-cond-badge">进行中</span></div>
            <div class="stage-name">Matthew Review<span class="stage-en">Verify investigation</span></div>
            <div class="stage-desc">
              <p class="stage-desc-zh"><strong>等你回答 6 个检查点</strong>，确认我没把现状搞错。回完才进 Step 3 写 SOP-1 v0.1。</p>
              <p class="stage-desc-en"><span class="lang-tag">EN</span> Answer 6 checkpoints → unblock writing</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stage-meta">
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">要回的</span> 调研笔记 §8 末尾 6 个检查点</div>
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">已答</span> 4/6 (剩 search skills 清单 + G-1/2/3 detail confirm)</div>
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">状态</span> <span class="chip chip-coral">等你 review</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stage-card stage-pending">
            <div class="stage-num">Step 3<span class="stage-cond-badge">待</span></div>
            <div class="stage-name">写 SOP-1 v0.1<span class="stage-en">Draft SOP doc</span></div>
            <div class="stage-desc">
              <p class="stage-desc-zh">中文为主 + 英文对照 · 目的 / 操作步骤 / 容易忽略的点 / 维护规则 4 section。</p>
              <p class="stage-desc-en"><span class="lang-tag">EN</span> Compose doc per ADMIN_DESIGN_SYSTEM rules + SOP-2 template</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stage-meta">
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">产出</span> <code>docs/SOP_1_INTAKE_DISCOVERY.md</code> + admin page 内容 fill</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stage-card stage-pending">
            <div class="stage-num">Step 4<span class="stage-cond-badge">待</span></div>
            <div class="stage-name">验证<span class="stage-en">Deploy verify</span></div>
            <div class="stage-desc">
              <p class="stage-desc-zh">astro build 本地通过 → push → GH Actions success → browser verify live URL + screenshot。</p>
              <p class="stage-desc-en"><span class="lang-tag">EN</span> Build + push + GH Actions + live URL marker + screenshot</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stage-meta">
              <div><span class="stage-meta-label">协议</span> SOP-X-Deploy (待写为正式 SOP)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="admin-note-line"><strong>📋 调研笔记 review 入口</strong>：<code>data/qa/sop-investigations/sop-1.md</code> §8 末尾 6 个检查点等你回。</p>
      </section>

      <!-- ─── 4 入口对比 (channel-flow pattern, SOP-2 同款) ─────────────── -->
      <section class="admin-paper-section">
        <div class="admin-paper-section-head">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">客户发现 · 4 个入口（含 Places enrichment）</p>
            <h2>从哪里抓客户 <span class="en-sub">4 entries to V2 entity store</span></h2>
          </div>
          <span class="admin-section-count">3 主入口 + 1 增强入口 · 全统一进 V2 entity store</span>
        </div>
        <p class="section-lede">不同来源最后<strong>必须统一进 V2 entity store</strong>。4 个入口形态不同，但 entity schema + 后续 pipeline 完全一致。<br/>
        📘 详见 <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-handoff-doc">SOP-1 → SOP-2 数据交接合约</a> · 🔧 工具清单见 <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-x-tooling">SOP-X-Tooling</a>。</p>

        <div class="channel-flow">
          <div class="channel-card channel-0">
            <div class="channel-stage">主入口 · 日常主力</div>
            <div class="channel-zh">🐳 gosom Docker scraper</div>
            <div class="channel-name"><code>localhost:8080</code> Docker container</div>
            <div class="channel-unit">1 batch 任务 = N leads (实测 20 leads / 3 分钟)</div>
            <div class="channel-purpose"><code>POST /api/v1/jobs</code> with keywords array → CSV → 转 JSONL → upsertDiscoveryRun → entity store</div>
            <div class="channel-meta">
              <span>✅ 免费 · 批量</span>
              <span>⚠ <code>max_time</code> ≥ 180s</span>
              <span>34 列 CSV 字段</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-arrow">
            <span class="channel-arrow-label">↓ 不同入口，相同 entity 形态</span>
            <span class="channel-arrow-glyph">▼</span>
          </div>

          <div class="channel-card channel-1">
            <div class="channel-stage">V2 入口 · image-lead</div>
            <div class="channel-zh">🖼 image-lead V2 (G-6 ✅)</div>
            <div class="channel-name"><code>npm run pl:ingest-image -- --image PATH --business-name X --phone Y --niche --city</code></div>
            <div class="channel-unit">1 张图片 (名片 / 店面 / 招牌) = 1 lead</div>
            <div class="channel-purpose">网上只能找到图片格式时的 ingest 路径 — 写入 <code>data/leads/entities/image_&lt;slug&gt;_&lt;phone&gt;.json</code>，与 gosom 同等 V2 公民。OCR 自动 extract = G-6.1 backlog。</div>
            <div class="channel-meta">
              <span>✅ V2 active 2026-05-12</span>
              <span>当前手填字段</span>
              <span>OCR auto-extract → G-6.1</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-arrow">
            <span class="channel-arrow-label">↓ 统一进 V2 entity store</span>
            <span class="channel-arrow-glyph">▼</span>
          </div>

          <div class="channel-card channel-2">
            <div class="channel-stage">实验入口 · 关键词 search</div>
            <div class="channel-zh">🔍 Search skill 系列</div>
            <div class="channel-name">多 search 引擎 (Tinyfish / DDGS / Doko / etc.)</div>
            <div class="channel-unit">1 关键词 query = N 搜索结果 → 提取商家信息</div>
            <div class="channel-purpose">当前与 gosom keywords[] 参数同源；未来"非 Google Maps search" 是 v0.2 范围</div>
            <div class="channel-meta">
              <span>🧪 实验 / 同源 gosom</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-arrow">
            <span class="channel-arrow-label">↓ grade ≥ B 才触发，控制成本</span>
            <span class="channel-arrow-glyph">▼</span>
          </div>

          <div class="channel-card channel-3">
            <div class="channel-stage">增强入口 · Places API (G-7 ✅)</div>
            <div class="channel-zh">📍 Google Places API enrichment</div>
            <div class="channel-name"><code>npm run pl:places-enrich -- --entity-key place_X</code></div>
            <div class="channel-unit">1 entity 增强 = 1 API call (Details Basic SKU, $0.017)</div>
            <div class="channel-purpose">SOP-2 detailed-audit 后 grade ≥ B 触发 → Places Details Basic call → 写入 <code>entity.latest.places_enrichment</code> (types[] 多分类 / E.164 国际电话 / 验证 opening_hours / photos 引用)</div>
            <div class="channel-meta">
              <span>✅ active 2026-05-12</span>
              <span>💰 $200/月免费额度 ≈ 11K calls (硬 cap 在 11K)</span>
              <span>📊 quota 见 <a href="/admin/scoring/sop-x-tooling">SOP-X-Tooling</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="admin-note-line"><strong>关键设计</strong>：不管哪条路进来，最后<strong>统一</strong>写到 <code>data/leads/entities/&lt;key&gt;.json</code> + <code>discovery-events.jsonl</code> + <code>queues.json</code> → 后续 SOP-2 筛选 + 审计 pipeline 完全一致。Places enrichment 是 grade≥B 后的增强，**不**改变 entity schema 主结构（只加 <code>latest.places_enrichment</code> 子对象）。</p>
      </section>

      <!-- ─── 10 容易忽略的点 + 3 待建工具 (admin-table pattern) ─────────── -->
      <section class="admin-paper-section">
        <div class="admin-paper-section-head">
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">容易忽略的点 + 待建工具</p>
            <h2>实战中的坑 <span class="en-sub">Gotchas + tools to build during SOP-1 implementation</span></h2>
          </div>
          <span class="admin-section-count">10 gotchas · 3 tools</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="subhead">① 10 个容易忽略的点</h3>
        <div class="admin-table-wrap">
          <table class="admin-table">
            <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>点</th><th>影响</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>1</td><td>Niche 是 substring match (含 "oof" → roofing)</td><td>偶尔误进 "Roofer's Bar"，cheap-audit SKIP 兜底</td></tr>
              <tr><td>2</td><td>同 lead 重复抓 → place_id dedup</td><td>自动合并 history，不污染 entity</td></tr>
              <tr><td>3</td><td>V1 status + V2 phase 两套状态字段共存</td><td>discovery 写 status，sales 状态机用 phase</td></tr>
              <tr><td>4</td><td>没 website 的 lead → starter_candidate</td><td>未完全自动化，要 SOP-2 §6 路径</td></tr>
              <tr><td>5</td><td>Image lead 走 V1 不进 V2</td><td>Matthew 已定要并入 V2 主流程</td></tr>
              <tr><td>6</td><td><code>max_time</code> ≥ 180 秒</td><td>gosom API hard limit，&lt; 180 直接 422</td></tr>
              <tr><td>7</td><td><strong>Contact identity 多触点缺失</strong></td><td>social / contact-us URL 没记 → SOP-ART-3</td></tr>
              <tr><td>8</td><td>sourceQuery 字段是关键追溯线</td><td>跨 niche/city 扩展时筛选靠这字段</td></tr>
              <tr><td>9</td><td>Discord forum tags 必须先 setup</td><td>tags 不存在 → applied_tags API 422</td></tr>
              <tr><td>10</td><td>GMB 没设 category → entity.latest.category 空</td><td>cheap-audit 会 SKIP，需手动 enrichment 补</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h3 class="subhead">② 3 个工具 SOP-1 实施时要建</h3>
        <div class="admin-table-wrap">
          <table class="admin-table">
            <thead><tr><th>ID</th><th>工具</th><th>用途</th><th>工程量</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td><code>G-1</code></td><td><code>pl:scrape-docker</code> CLI</td><td>POST job → poll → CSV → JSONL → upsertDiscoveryRun (现在没有，每次都手动)</td><td>~1h</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>G-2</code></td><td><code>pl:preflight</code> CLI</td><td>跑 batch 前 30 秒健康检查：Docker / API / Discord / claude_cli / 磁盘</td><td>~30min</td></tr>
              <tr><td><code>G-3</code></td><td>Entity schema 加 <code>batch_id</code></td><td>mergeLeadIntoEntity + bridge 透传，每 lead 知道"我哪批进来的"</td><td>~20min</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <p class="admin-note-line">完整调研笔记在 <code>data/qa/sop-investigations/sop-1.md</code> (~280 行)。<strong>请打开 review 后回答 6 个检查点 (§8 末尾)</strong>，确认我没搞错现状，我才写 SOP-1 v0.1。</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>


<style>
  /* Page-specific layout only. All visual chrome from admin-design-system.css. */
  .sop-shell { max-width: 1080px; }
  .sop-shell .admin-header h1 { font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.15; }
</style>
